ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>劇情峰迴路轉幾得意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想睇gay post 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫埋呢個寫gay故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係真先好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d042b03403d8beab15884af81fa3afd07c9bdd","tid":214264,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:17:39.000Z","msg":"「你話咩話？」佢吃了一驚。<br />\n<br />\n「我⋯⋯」深知得罪了阿偉，我都慌了。<br />\n<br />\n「你跟我過嚟！」阿偉皺著眉頭，在我還未回神過來時，他便捉住我的手，強行把我拉進了廁格。<br />\n<br />\n「喂喂！做咩事呀？喂⋯⋯」我被他逼到絕路，嚇得我兩行淚水直湧出來。<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻⋯⋯」阿偉奸笑一聲，再道：「我要教你打飛機呀。」<br />\n<br />\n「吓，咩呀⋯⋯」我柔弱的說。<br />\n<br />\n平時的M男，此時竟爾轉守為攻。<br />\n<br />\n我的心更加慌，不知他會做出甚麼事情。<br />\n<br />\n「唔使啦，我都冇飛機。」我微微一笑，想走過他身旁，逃離廁格之際⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n卻被他輕輕一推，逼回困境之中。<br />\n<br />\n「想走？」阿偉奸笑著說：「你今日點都要幫我打一次飛機㗎啦！」<br />\n<br />\n說罷，他便脫下褲子，露出那藏着已久的龐然巨物。"}]}